<li>持續採用 io.js 在你的應用程式之中。</li>
</ul>
<p>原文：<a href="https://medium.com/node-js-javascript/io-js-week-of-february-13th-2015-7846b94074a2" target="_blank" rel="external">io.js Week of February 13th 2015</a>，作者：<a href="https://medium.com/@iojs" target="_blank" rel="external">@iojs</a>，翻譯 <a href="https://github.com/iojs/iojs-tw" target="_blank" rel="external">@iojs-tw</a>，授權 <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/deed.zh_TW" target="_blank" rel="external">CC-BY 4.0</a></p>
